snippet.title: PVKK: Planetenverteidigungskanonenkommandant - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
If that intrigues you, wishlist PVKK here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2956040
To talk about PVKK join our Discord: https://discord.gg/AxYpX7AaFP

Operate your planetary defense cannon to fend off an interplanetary invasion from the comfort of your cozy bunker. You’re here to stay, so obey your superiors, press the right buttons, and sip your daily tea ration - it's good for you.
